[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0684","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0684.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0891","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 Download Behavior 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 的下载行为（Download Behavior）功能存在安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造特制的服务端重定向（server-side redirect）响应，诱使用户访问恶意网页后绕过 IE 5 的安全限制，实现跨域读取目标系统上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5 版本，攻击成功的前提是受害者使用受影响浏览器访问攻击者控制的恶意站点，无需额外认证，可能导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0891"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.310","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.5 以上版本，该漏洞在 IE 5.5 及后续版本中已修复。如无法升级，建议禁用 ActiveX 控件及脚本下载行为：在 Internet 选项 → 安全 → 自定义级别中，将\"下载已签名的 ActiveX 控件\"和\"下载未签名的 ActiveX 控件\"均设为\"禁用\"。根本解决措施是停止使用已停止支持的 Internet Explorer，迁移至 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ242542","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-002.shtml","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/37828","http://www.osvdb.org/11274","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/674","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-040","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19530"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0684.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0400","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0400.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0705","title":"ISC INN inews 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器中的 inews 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的新闻组文章数据触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而可能造成拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 ISC INN 2.2 及 RedHat Linux 6.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0705"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.177","remediation":"升级 ISC INN 至 2.3 及以上版本，或安装 RedHat Linux 6.0 对应安全补丁 (RHSA-1999:034)。如无法升级，可移除 inews 的 setuid 权限 (chmod -s /usr/bin/inews) 并限制仅受信用户通过 SSH 提交新闻文章作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/616","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19480","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0705","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0705.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-43p9-vj97-wmgv/GHSA-43p9-vj97-wmgv.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/inn.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/616/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990907.data","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0400.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0202","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0670","title":"Eyedog ActiveX 控件缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Eyedog ActiveX 控件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造特制网页诱使用户访问，触发缓冲区溢出从而执行任意命令。该漏洞影响了 Internet Explorer 浏览器中集成的 Eyedog ActiveX 控件，攻击者需要诱导用户打开恶意网页或包含恶意内容的电子邮件才能成功利用，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0670"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.737","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 于 1999 年 8 月发布的安全公告 MS99-032 对应补丁（KB240308），或通过 Windows Update 更新至最新版本的 Internet Explorer。该补丁为 Eyedog ActiveX 控件设置 kill bit，阻止其在 IE 中加载。作为手动缓解措施，可在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 下为 CLSID {A5ECB622-137C-11D2-B34D-00C04FB6F6E1} 创建 Compatibility Flags 值为 0x400 的 DWORD 项，同样可禁用该控件。长远建议升级至现代操作系统及浏览器，因较新版本已不再包含此控件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-032","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0670","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0670.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88352/info.html","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0196","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0196.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0669","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4/5 ActiveX Eyedog 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0/5.0 中的 Eyedog ActiveX 控件被错误标记为\"对脚本安全\"，远程攻击者可构造恶意网页或 HTML 邮件，诱使用户在 IE 中访问即可直接调用该控件执行任意命令，无需用户交互点击附件。该漏洞因 Bubbleboy 蠕虫的利用而闻名，影响 IE 4.0 及 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 4.0，属于中危漏洞。微软已发布相关安全公告并提供修复措施。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0669"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.617","remediation":"在注册表中为 Eyedog ActiveX 控件设置 killbit（CLSID: {00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000}），将 Internet 区域安全级别设为\"高\"并禁用 ActiveX 脚本。升级至 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本，或迁移至现代浏览器（Edge/Chrome/Firefox）以彻底消除风险。对于仍使用 IE 的遗留系统，通过组策略禁用所有标记为\"对脚本安全\"的未签名 ActiveX 控件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19487","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0669.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0669","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0669.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0669.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m9vr-8q37-f2rh/GHSA-m9vr-8q37-f2rh.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0669.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--231fc8ca-ffbe-47b7-994f-ed5754a27cb7.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0196.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0196.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0196.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0503","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0503.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0774","title":"Martin Stover Mars NWE 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Mars NetWare Emulation (NWE, mars_nwe) 0.99 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向受影响系统提供特制的超长目录名触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，可能造成拒绝服务或权限提升。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，建议用户尽快升级至最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0774"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.833","remediation":"升级 mars_nwe 至 0.99 以上版本（如 0.99pl18+ 或最新 CVS 快照），该版本已修复长目录名处理代码中的缓冲区边界检查缺失问题。如无法升级，可在 mars_nwe.conf 中限制 NFS 导出目录路径长度不超过 255 字符，并限制可登录用户范围，同时利用系统审计工具监控 mars_nwe 进程的异常崩溃行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/617","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19485"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0503.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1209","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0911","title":"ProFTPd MKD/CWD 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ProFTPd 1.2 pre1 至 pre5 版本、wu-ftpd 及 beroftpd 中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送一系列精心构造的 MKD（创建目录）和 CWD（切换目录）命令，创建深层嵌套目录结构，触发缓冲区溢出，进而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响多个主流 FTP 服务端软件，危害严重，无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0911"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.797","remediation":"升级 ProFTPd 至 1.2.0 RC1 或更高稳定版本（1.2.0pre 系列已停止支持），该漏洞在 1.2.0 RC1 中修复。使用 wu-ftpd 的用户应升级至 2.6.2 或更新版本，或在 inetd 配置中禁用匿名用户 MKD/CWD 目录创建权限作为临时缓解措施。beroftpd 用户建议迁移至已维护的 FTP 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1999/19990210","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/612","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19476"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0866","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1016","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer HTML Form Control 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 及 FrontPage Express、Outlook Express 5、Eudora 等软件所使用的 HTML Form Control 组件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造包含超大表单输入字段（如表格单元格中的大量文本框）的恶意网页或 HTML 邮件，诱使用户访问后导致目标系统 CPU 占用率高达 100%，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需认证即可触发，影响范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1016"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.717","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 或更高版本可修复此漏洞。对于仍使用旧版 IE 的环境，建议禁用 Active Scripting 及在 Outlook Express 中阻止 HTML 邮件加载表单控件。现网用户应迁移至受支持的现代浏览器（如 Edge、Chrome）以免受此及其他已知漏洞影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93578772920970&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/606","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19471","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1016.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1016","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/e7c7a6140bbd6a60ea622b6124620fbed9d12332/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-33jr-59q9-j8vq/GHSA-33jr-59q9-j8vq.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_nt_ms02-005.nasl","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1016.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0736","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0736.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0939","title":"Debian Linux epic/epic4 IRC客户端 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Debian Linux 2.1 和 2.2 版本中附带的 epic/epic4 IRC 客户端存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向客户端发送特制的超长字符串，触发客户端崩溃或无法响应，导致正常的 IRC 通信服务中断。该漏洞无需认证即可利用，攻击复杂度低，虽未造成数据泄露或代码执行，但严重影响服务的可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0939"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.163","remediation":"升级 epic4 到 2.8 以上版本（Debian 2.1/2.2 已 EOL，建议升级到 Debian 3.0 Woody 或更新版本，其中包含已修复的 epic4 包）；也可改用 irssi、weechat 等替代 IRC 客户端，或在 IRC 服务器端限制单条消息最大长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/605"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0736.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1018","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1235","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 FTP 密码信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 存在 FTP 凭据泄露漏洞。当用户通过 FTP 协议访问服务器时，程序将用户名和密码以明文形式记录在浏览器历史记录（index.dat）中，未进行任何加密或脱敏处理。本地攻击者可读取其他用户的 index.dat 文件，从中提取 FTP 账户信息；物理接近的攻击者也可通过肩窥方式，在用户鼠标悬停于 FTP 链接时从浏览器状态栏直接获取凭据。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1235"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.410","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本可缓解密码明文记录问题；根本解决方案是使用专用 FTP 客户端（如 FileZilla）替代 IE 访问 FTP 站点，并避免在 URL 历史中保留密码。使用后建议及时清除 IE 历史记录，并对敏感 FTP 站点启用加密传输（SFTP/FTPS）。作为安全基线，应停止使用已停止安全支持的 IE 版本，迁移至现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ntbugtraq.ntadvice.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9904&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R179","http://packetderm.cotse.com/mailing-lists/ntbugtraq/1999/0364.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3289","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19473","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1235","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1235.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v7w3-r9q2-mwx4/GHSA-v7w3-r9q2-mwx4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87772/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000751.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fe06dc37-1641-4571-a309-13ef3dac15ec.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0669","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0669.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0872","title":"Vixie Cron 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie cron 在处理 crontab 文件中的 MAILTO 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可创建包含超长 MAILTO 字符串的特制 crontab 文件触发溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 OpenLinux 等多种 Linux 发行版中的 Vixie cron 服务，攻击者需拥有本地用户权限即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0872"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.990","remediation":"升级 Vixie cron 至 3.0pl1 或更高版本，该版本已限制 crontab 中 MAILTO 环境变量的最大长度，防止缓冲区溢出导致权限提升。如无法立即升级，可暂时移除 crontab 文件中所有 MAILTO 赋值语句作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/611","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/759"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0669.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0489","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0769","title":"ISC Vixie Cron MAILTO 环境变量本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 在处理 MAILTO 环境变量时存在参数注入漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置特制的 MAILTO 环境变量向 sendmail 命令传递恶意参数，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenLinux 2.2、Debian 2.1/2.2、RedHat 6.0 等 Linux 发行版，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0769"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.193","remediation":"Red Hat 6.0 用户升级 cron 包至 3.0pl1-24 及以上版本（RHSA-1999:023）；Debian 2.1/2.2 用户升级 cron 包至 3.0pl1-47 及以上版本；Caldera OpenLinux 2.2 用户应用厂商发布的 cron 安全补丁。升级后 cron 将 MAILTO 值仅作为收件地址处理，不再允许传递额外参数给 sendmail。如无法升级，可移除 crontab 中不受信任用户的 MAILTO 设置或限制 cron 的使用权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/611","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19474"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0483","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0768","title":"红帽 (Red Hat) 和 SUSE Linux Vixie Cron 服务 MAILTO 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 在处理 MAILTO 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长 MAILTO 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 RedHat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 及 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.0/6.1 等系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制 cron 任务的 MAILTO 变量长度。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0768"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.067","remediation":"立即升级 vixie-cron 至 3.0.1-56 及以上版本（Red Hat）或安装 SUSE 对应安全补丁；若无法升级，在 crontab 中避免使用 MAILTO 变量或限制 MAILTO 值长度不超过 256 字节；建议迁移至现代 Linux 发行版（如 RHEL 8+），其 cronie 已内置该漏洞修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/602","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19470"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0905","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1052","title":"Microsoft FrontPage 表单结果文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage 默认将表单提交结果存储在网站根目录下的 `/_private/form_results.txt` 文件中，该文件权限设置为世界可读且位于 Web 文档根目录内，导致任何能够访问该网站的远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接通过浏览器读取其他用户提交的敏感表单数据（如密码、个人信息等）。此漏洞危害中等，影响使用 Microsoft FrontPage 创建的网站。缓解措施包括更改默认存储路径或限制该文件的访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1052"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.350","remediation":"将 FrontPage 表单结果存储路径从默认的 `/_private/` 目录修改为 Web 根目录之外的路径（如 `C:\\fp_formdata\\`），并通过 IIS 权限设置拒绝匿名用户对 `form_results.txt` 的读取权限。如使用 Apache，在 `.htaccess` 中添加 `<FilesMatch \"form_results\\.txt\"> Deny from all</FilesMatch>` 规则。建议迁移至更新的 Web 开发平台（如 ASP.NET/PHP），因 FrontPage 已停止维护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582550911564&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1052","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch.json","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88081/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0320","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0320.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0720","title":"GNU glibc pt_chown 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"GNU glibc 2.1/2.1.1 版本中的 pt_chown 工具存在权限管理缺陷，该工具以 setuid 权限运行，未充分校验调用者身份即可修改 TTY 终端设备的属主。本地低权限攻击者可通过精心构造的参数利用 pt_chown 将任意 TTY 设备所有权改为自身，实现对其他用户终端会话的监控或劫持，从而获取敏感信息或提升至目标用户权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0720"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.947","remediation":"升级 glibc 至 2.1.2 或更高版本；如无法升级，执行 `chmod -s /usr/libexec/pt_chown` 移除 setuid 权限位，或直接删除 pt_chown 二进制文件以彻底阻断利用路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/597","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=lcamtuf.4.05.9907041223290.355-300000%40nimue.ids.pl","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19467"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0320.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0320.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1689","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1689.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1064","title":"WindowMaker 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"WindowMaker 0.52 至 0.60.0 版本存在多个缓冲区溢出漏洞。当以超长程序名（argv[0]）执行 WindowMaker 时，攻击者可触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标系统拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。受影响版本范围较广，攻击条件简单，无需复杂认证即可利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1064"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.880","remediation":"建议升级 WindowMaker 至 0.61.0 或更高版本，当前最新稳定版 0.96.0 已彻底修复该 argv[0] 缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可采用以下缓解措施：(1) 使用 grsecurity/PaX 内核补丁开启地址空间布局随机化（ASLR）和不可执行内存页（NX）；(2) 在启动包装脚本中校验传入 argv[0] 长度，截断超长程序名后调用 WindowMaker；(3) 禁止在 SetUID 或网络暴露环境中运行 WindowMaker。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93555317429630&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582070508957&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/596","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1064","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1064.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8xf-jm9x-c783/GHSA-q8xf-jm9x-c783.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/596/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1064.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_u